  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>&lt;프로그래머스&gt; 자릿수 더하기</title>
    <link href="http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/06/programmers-038/"/>
    <id>http://mjae404.github.io/2024/05/06/programmers-038/</id>
    <published>2024-05-06T10:39:37.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-06T10:52:13.877Z</updated>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;정수 &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt;이 매개변수로 주어질 때 &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt;의 각 자리 숫자의 합을 return하도록 solution 함수를 완성해주세요.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;0 ≤ &lt;code&gt;n&lt;/code&gt; ≤ 1,000,000&lt;/li&gt;
